data.description: Welcome Home to this beautiful 4 bed 3 bath custom brick over block pool home!  From the moment you pull through the wrought iron gate you will fall in love with this completely remodeled private escape!  As you enter you'll notice the open floor plan with vaulted ceilings and solar tubes in the living room for added natural light.  Brand new "Pinterest" gourmet kitchen with a gorgeous hammered copper farmhouse double basin sink, seamless granite island, stainless steel appliances, wine fridge and plenty of cabinets!  New porcelain tile "wood look" floors throughout the main areas.  Newly remodeled Master Bathroom with a double sink vanity, granite countertop, jetted bathtub.  Bedrooms 2, 3 share remodeled bathroom with granite counters.  The 4th bedroom/loft upstairs has a full bathroom.  Enjoy those hot summer days in your 15x30 salt water pool.  Plantation shutters are in the kitchen and the sitting room out to the pool.  Enjoy the views from the lanai of the beautiful trees with no neighbors behind you!  On those cool winter nights, sit by the fire pit to warm up.  There are plenty of activities for the family:  play set in the backyard, custom made steel swing set, air conditioned "Kid Cabin" above the potting shed, and a half-court basketball court!  There is a 2 vehicle carport and an add'l 12 x 20 out building.  Close to shopping but tucked away in the woods!  The only thing this gorgeous home needs is YOU!
data.whatILove: Recently remodeled with newer kitchen and new roof, paint, carpet, and fence. Two Sheds large shaded tree lot. Lots of privacy. County living with chicken coop.
